question.title: Cannot execute -h\bin\java to determine the version
question.body:
Steps to reproduce

  1. set JAVA_HOME variable to C:\Program Files\Android\Android Studio\jbr
  2. run PS C:\> flutter doctor --android-licenses
  3. get the error
  4. try to set JAVA_HOME variable to C:\Program Files\Java\jdk-23
  5. get the same error

Actual results

PS C:\Users\tri36> flutter doctor --android-licenses
